        <Text tag="p" variant="textLG" class="text-base-400 mt-4">
          Whether you're a corporate seeking CSR advisory, an NGO looking for technology solutions, or a foundation planning impact assessmentâ€”we're here to partner with you.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </div>
